.IP "\(bu" 2
\fCGLM_FORCE_PRECISION_HIGHP_FLOAT\fP: High precision (default)
.PP
.PP
Available defines for floating point types (\fCglm::dvec\\*\fP, \fCglm::dmat\\*\fP):
.PP
