\fCGLM_FORCE_PRECISION_LOWP_DOUBLE\fP: Low precision
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fCGLM_FORCE_PRECISION_MEDIUMP_DOUBLE\fP: Medium precision
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fCGLM_FORCE_PRECISION_HIGHP_DOUBLE\fP: High precision (default)
.PP
.PP
Available defines for signed integer types (\fCglm::ivec\\*\fP):
.PP
